        <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">How it works</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Scroll through a feed of photos within a specific location or worldwide. Users are free to post photos within their locations feed or the worldwide feed and interact with each other on a worldwide scale through up votes, down votes, and comments. Essentially, every photo posted is entered into two competitions; a local competition and a worldwide competition. 
        This gives users the opportunity to play for two prizes at once!</p>
      </div>
